<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">〔仕上げ〕</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<list>
<listItem>
<sentence><enclosedCharacter description="○">４６</enclosedCharacter>　<enclosedCharacter description="○">４７</enclosedCharacter>―いよいよ仕上げに入ります。</sentence>
<sentence>例によって気持ちを新たにして作業に臨みましょう。</sentence>
<sentence>光背の形から各部分の隅々まで、丁寧に仕上げて下さい。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<figureBlock>
<figure>
</figure>
<caption>
<sentence type="quasi"><enclosedCharacter description="○">４６</enclosedCharacter></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</caption>
</figureBlock>
<figureBlock>
